  <Dialog id="0" name="MSG_000_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 6 4 52 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 1 0 0}I found it. It's at the south end of the Moonlight Bridge.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 6 4 52 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 2 0 0}The twelfth and final Shadow...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="1" name="MSG_001_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 222 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 3 0 0}Mmm, so this is it...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="2" name="MSG_002_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 6 3 52 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 4 0 0}And as we expected, I'm detecting more Persona-users nearby...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 6 3 52 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 5 0 0}It's Strega.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="3" name="MSG_003_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 6 0 0}They know this is their last chance. We expected as much, but don't be careless.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="4" name="MSG_004_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 8 2 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 7 0 0}So it's them...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="5" name="MSG_005_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0004"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 4 9 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 8 0 0}Heh. Saves us the trouble of looking for them.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="6" name="MSG_006_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 9 0 0}You've all fought admirably thus far.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 10 0 0}This will be our last operation. Let's all come back safely.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="7" name="MSG_007_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 2 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 11 0 0}Got it.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="8" name="MSG_008_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0006"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 9 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 12 0 0}Roger that.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="9" name="MSG_009_0_0" type="Message">
